{"tid":2030136,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【對沖人生】香港恐似西藏命運 - 錢志健","createTime":"2020-05-22T14:45:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T03:57:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"95088c646b853c16ce566550907cfa02ddaf765c","tid":2030136,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:45:17.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200522/6LZEIMSGO3JXQUP2LT37CAKYI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200522%2F6LZEIMSGO3JXQUP2LT37CAKYI4%2F&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CKmkGRIJ7ARjMQoHd6uTSg0%3D&h=c0ea59c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200522%2F6LZEIMSGO3JXQUP2LT37CAKYI4%2F&h=38e58da1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20200522/6LZEIMSGO3JXQUP2LT37CAKYI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n【對沖人生】香港恐似西藏命運 - 錢志健<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200522/large/1590078190_2362.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200522%2Flarge%2F1590078190_2362.jpg&h=ee047ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第十四世達賴喇嘛。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n林鄭政府推卸責任，抹殺港人對「兩制」最後希望。監警會變了「撐警會」，港台節目「頭條新聞」被下架及快停播，香港價值蠶食之快，大家有目共睹。筆者的共黨「半生熟」之交，只是「默默地」部署資產轉移及套現；不大關心政治的中產，也明白到香港的這股政治低氣壓。<br />\n<br />\n筆者四年前的九月中，在比利時布魯塞爾，獲西藏流亡政府達賴喇嘛14世尊者接見，談到香港問題。這是「佔中」及傘運後的兩年。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n打一些關鍵字，你們可以在《蘋果日報》看到整段詳細報道。重點如下：談到香港情況，達賴喇嘛以自己和西藏流亡政府為例，指西藏人至今己抗爭60年，但從未失去希望。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩年內變「中央直轄市」<br />\n<br />\n中共兩會在北京進行中，「港版國安法」或殺到。港區人大陳女士日前公佈她的兩會提案，有書面建議給北京，訂立《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區維護國家安全法》，直接依基本法第十八條，將國。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n一撮投資者在二月至三月武肺大崩跌下身家大縮水、工作被消失或減鐘。更大的「陰乾式」動作，是港人全方位的自由被箝制：預計到六四、七一遊行會被勒令停止。由上年11月的中大、理大捍衛戰，。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n最後，時局不穩，把各種資產套現，要快做好安排。港府正在發癲，政權為所欲為，繼續和香港人攬炒。究竟香港人的命運，是否和西藏。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n錢志健<br />\n資深對沖基金經理<br />\nmailto:mdehedgecenter@gmail.com<br />\n本欄逢周五刊出"},{"pid":"51e017c2054a0e0e96cf7d75a3ee95a1d526037f","tid":2030136,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"下一步換血"},{"pid":"93cdc13c3646ddb3ed6b7818b42fffabe25bf90a","tid":2030136,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:00:31.000Z","msg":"車志健我就識"},{"pid":"1aee9cbc1227050ab13ee261dae66d62c6108b51","tid":2030136,"uid":76398,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"51e017c2054a0e0e96cf7d75a3ee95a1d526037f","tid":2030136,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"下一步換血"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"羅家聰話金融已經換得7788"},{"pid":"c3b55bc3e90c15d2179b26074be234f3fd4f8ccc","tid":2030136,"uid":7343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1aee9cbc1227050ab13ee261dae66d62c6108b51","tid":2030136,"uid":76398,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"51e017c2054a0e0e96cf7d75a3ee95a1d526037f","tid":2030136,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"下一步換血"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"羅家聰話金融已經換得7788"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:04:33.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n高級工種到中層大多都係蝗"},{"pid":"948421f4fe7a5498ae023b50a0dfe11a77fd3ff1","tid":2030136,"uid":350320,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1aee9cbc1227050ab13ee261dae66d62c6108b51","tid":2030136,"uid":76398,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"51e017c2054a0e0e96cf7d75a3ee95a1d526037f","tid":2030136,"uid":7343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"下一步換血"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:03:30.000Z","msg":"羅家聰話金融已經換得7788"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T14:06:21.000Z","msg":"ibank front office 大部份mainland已經一段時間。<br />\n而加中資bank back office都請mainlans 先"},{"pid":"2ccdca12ec1517ed88b1ff44b534bf09bc48a9c4","tid":2030136,